create or replace table dbt_adventureworks_dwh.dim_credit_card
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
    location 'none/dim_credit_card'
      

      as
      with stg_salesorderheader as (
    select distinct creditcardid
    from dbt_adventureworks_seed.salesorderheader
    where creditcardid is not null
),

stg_creditcard as (
    select *
    from dbt_adventureworks_seed.creditcard
)

select
    
    
md5(cast(concat(coalesce(cast(stg_salesorderheader.creditcardid as string), '_dbt_utils_surrogate_key_null_')) as string)) as creditcard_key,
    stg_salesorderheader.creditcardid,
    stg_creditcard.cardtype
from stg_salesorderheader
left join stg_creditcard on stg_salesorderheader.creditcardid = stg_creditcard.creditcardid

create or replace table dbt_adventureworks_dwh.dim_customer
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
    location 'none/dim_customer'
      

      as
      with stg_customer as (
    select
        customerid,
        personid,
        storeid
    from dbt_adventureworks_seed.customer
),

stg_person as (
    select
        businessentityid,
        concat(coalesce(firstname, ''), ' ', coalesce(middlename, ''), ' ', coalesce(lastname, '')) as fullname
    from dbt_adventureworks_seed.person
),

stg_store as (
    select
        businessentityid as storebusinessentityid,
        storename
    from dbt_adventureworks_seed.store
)

select
    
    
md5(cast(concat(coalesce(cast(stg_customer.customerid as string), '_dbt_utils_surrogate_key_null_')) as string)) as customer_key,
    stg_customer.customerid,
    stg_person.businessentityid,
    stg_person.fullname,
    stg_store.storebusinessentityid,
    stg_store.storename
from stg_customer
left join stg_person on stg_customer.personid = stg_person.businessentityid
left join stg_store on stg_customer.storeid = stg_store.storebusinessentityid

create or replace table dbt_adventureworks_dwh.dim_product

      as
      with stg_product as (
    select *
    from dbt_adventureworks_seed.product
),

stg_product_subcategory as (
    select *
    from dbt_adventureworks_seed.productsubcategory
),

stg_product_category as (

select
